{"tid":2258932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】黃店識嘅啊姐借錢唔還，點算？","createTime":"2020-10-26T12:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T05:01:31.000Z","uid":317157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"872235d421e8613ec8a9caf7f188404427db63ee","tid":2258932,"uid":317157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"話說前排6月係九龍灣一間幾出名嘅黃店兼職<br />\n有個啊姐幾friendly 有講有笑咁<br />\n有日飯飯佢就同我講佢老公係長期病患者<br />\n咁啱佢又前幾日就俾人偷左個袋<br />\n冇曬卡冇曬身份證<br />\n冇錢幫佢老公買藥喎<br />\n講到有咁慘得咁慘 唔幫佢就出人命咁<br />\n衰心軟就借左5千俾佢<br />\n佢都話過幾日就有得還<br />\n<br />\n過幾日佢又真係還喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係還2千<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如是者個3千就一直拖一直拖<br />\n拖都算啦 <br />\n你老味仲要日日拍曬心口話聽日還到 叫我放心<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢依家職都遲埋<br />\n我得佢個名同電話<br />\n都預左個3千當係交學費㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過又有d唔甘心&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最仆街係發現佢偽黃<br />\n當做善事都唔順氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇師兄有d咩想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd54df5a1f3a64441f4a7e8288eb420e5892d37","tid":2258932,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"黃即正義<br />\n當捐咗612"},{"pid":"9125b03aa9bf0d7606d546eb44499c42d68826b3","tid":2258932,"uid":2002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"黃唔代表好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主都幾好人 唔識都借到5000"},{"pid":"62b08b823a28228f21bc4ba05fd156f2c175d1af","tid":2258932,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:11:04.000Z","msg":"P牌食屎啦"},{"pid":"8ef209da8cc4a9b8bdf2efa1feee6c13a768429a","tid":2258932,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"